JOHANNESBURG, May 26 – The South African Football Association (Safa) have announced their nominations for the referees awards which will be made at the annual ceremony in Sandton, Johannesburg, on Tuesday. They will join the nominees for various PSL players’ award categories announced recently. The complete list of nominations: Referee of the Season: Christopher Harrison, Victor Hlungwani, Victor Gomes Assistant Referee of the Season: Johannes Moshidi, Zakhele Siwela, Athenkosi Ndongeni Goalkeeper of the Season: Itumeleng Khune, Richard Ofori, Denis Onyango Defender of the Season: Bevan Fransman, Innocent Maela, Siyanda Xulu Midfielder of the Season: Siphesihle Ndlovu, Hlompho Kekana, Musa Nyatama Young Player of Season: Sibusiso Mabiliso, Teboho Mokoena, Siphesihle Ndlovu Player’s Player of the Season: Siphesihle Ndlovu, Percy Tau, Musa Nyatama Footballer of the Season: Hlompho Kekana, Siphesihle Ndlovu, Percy Tau.